♂ (
Figs. 46 d , 47 d
). Very similar to ♀ , but distinctly smaller (body length 49.0–60.0 mm). The ventral side of the femora can be dull yellow to straw, but also black. Vomer with the basal half broad, then abruptly narrowed to form an elongate, slender and gently up-curving terminal hook. Poculum small and flat, reaching to centre of anal segment, posterior margin rounded with median incision.
